review_data.title: Fantastic Experience
review_data.content: My family of 4 had dinner at this food joint. Several choices of Mediterranean specialty foods are available on the menu. Service is extremely courteous, ambiance is cozy and pricing is very reasonable. Taste of food is great. Would certainly very highly recommend this food...More

review_data.title: Mediterranean Cuisine option
review_data.content: The small restaurant is well located at the downtown. It is attended by its owner. Food is excellent and the service is kind and friendly. It is not luxury place but it is a good option when find good food with quick attention. Recommended.
